## 6. Intraday Feature Engineering (V2)

### 6.1 Per-Bar Features (25 features per minute bar)

| # | Feature | Formula / Description |
|---|---------|----------------------|
| 1 | `log_return` | log(Close_t / Close_{t-1}) |
| 2 | `volume_ratio` | Volume_t / EMA_20(Volume) |
| 3 | `vwap_distance` | (Close - cumulative_VWAP) / VWAP |
| 4 | `ema_9_distance` | (Close - EMA_9) / EMA_9 |
| 5 | `ema_20_distance` | (Close - EMA_20) / EMA_20 |
| 6 | `rsi_14` | 14-bar RSI |
| 7 | `bb_zscore` | (Close - BB_mid) / (BB_upper - BB_mid) |
| 8 | `bb_width` | (BB_upper - BB_lower) / BB_mid |
| 9 | `body_ratio` | abs(C-O) / (H-L+1e-10) — candle body proportion |
| 10 | `upper_shadow_ratio` | (H - max(O,C)) / (H-L+1e-10) |
| 11 | `lower_shadow_ratio` | (min(O,C) - L) / (H-L+1e-10) |
| 12 | `spread_pct` | (H-L) / C — intrabar volatility |
| 13 | `cum_volume_pct` | cumsum(Volume) / typical_day_volume |
| 14 | `time_normalized` | (minutes_since_930) / 375 — position in session |
| 15 | `orb_high_dist` | (Close - ORB_high) / ORB_range |
| 16 | `orb_low_dist` | (Close - ORB_low) / ORB_range |
| 17 | `day_return` | (Close - day_open) / day_open |
| 18 | `momentum_5` | Close / Close_{t-5} - 1 |
| 19 | `momentum_20` | Close / Close_{t-20} - 1 |
| 20 | `vol_momentum` | (up_volume_20 - down_volume_20) / total_volume_20 |
| 21 | `atr_14` | 14-bar ATR / Close — normalized |
| 22 | `close_vs_day_range` | (Close - day_low) / (day_high - day_low) |
| 23 | `session_volatility` | rolling_std(log_return, 20) |
| 24 | `obv_slope` | linear regression slope of OBV over 20 bars |
| 25 | `trade_intensity` | Volume × spread — proxy for institutional activity |

### 6.2 Session-Level Context Features (20 features, static per session)

These are computed once at session start from daily data:

| # | Feature | Description |
|---|---------|-------------|
| 1-4 | `prev_day_rsi`, `prev_day_macd`, `prev_day_macd_hist`, `prev_day_bb_zscore` | Yesterday's daily indicators |
| 5-6 | `prev_day_trend_strength`, `prev_day_regime` | Trend context |
| 7-8 | `prev_day_volatility_21`, `prev_day_adx` | Volatility context |
| 9 | `overnight_return` | (Today's open - Yesterday's close) / Yesterday's close |
| 10 | `gap_size` | Absolute overnight gap as % |
| 11 | `gap_direction` | +1 (gap up), -1 (gap down), 0 (flat) |
| 12 | `prev_day_close_location` | Where yesterday closed relative to its range |
| 13 | `prev_day_volume_zscore` | Yesterday's volume vs 20-day average |
| 14 | `day_of_week` | 0-4 (Monday-Friday) one-hot |
| 15 | `is_expiry_week` | F&O expiry week flag |
| 16 | `is_monthly_expiry` | Monthly expiry flag |
| 17 | `is_result_season` | Earnings season flag |
| 18 | `days_since_52w_high` | Days since 52-week high |
| 19 | `days_since_52w_low` | Days since 52-week low |
| 20 | `avg_intraday_range` | 20-day average of (High-Low)/Close |

